#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/EditorSettingsPanel.tsx:591
msgid "The settings in this editor cover the most commonly used options for most stores. However, many additional settings are available. Once you\\'ve saved any changes, head over to the CheckoutWC menu in your WordPress dashboard to explore more options."
msgstr "Indstillingerne i denne editor dækker de mest almindeligt anvendte muligheder for de fleste butikker. Der er dog mange yderligere indstillinger tilgængelige. Når du har gemt ændringer, kan du gå til CheckoutWC-menuen i dit WordPress-dashboard for at udforske flere muligheder."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/DesignSettingsPanel.tsx:55
msgid "Changing the template here updates the global CheckoutWC template selection used for logo, colors, and other design settings."
msgstr "Ændring af skabelonen her opdaterer det globale CheckoutWC-skabelonvalg, der bruges til logo, farver og andre designindstillinger."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/DesignSettingsPanel.tsx:120
msgid "Choose the logo you wish to display in the header."
msgstr "Vælg det logo, du ønsker at vise i headeren."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/DesignSettingsPanel.tsx:130
msgid "Automatically show and hide labels."
msgstr "Vis etiketter automatisk og skjul dem igen."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/DesignSettingsPanel.tsx:199
msgid "Add Custom CSS rules to control the appearance of the checkout template."
msgstr "Tilføj brugerdefinerede CSS-regler for at kontrollere udseendet af checkout-skabelonen."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:46
msgid "Adds a review step after payment information before finalizing order."
msgstr "Tilføjer et gennemgangstrin efter betalingsoplysninger før ordren afsluttes."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:53
msgid "Show all checkout steps on one page. Useful for digital stores."
msgstr "Vis alle checkout-trin på én side. Nyttigt for digitale butikker."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:65
msgid "WooCommerce has a habit of not selecting the free shipping method if it is setup to be conditionally enabled."
msgstr "WooCommerce har en tendens til ikke at vælge gratis fragtmetode, hvis den er sat op til at blive aktiveret betinget."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:76
msgid "Normally the login modal automatically opens if the entered email address matches an existing account."
msgstr "Normalt åbnes login-modal automatisk, hvis den indtastede e-mailadresse matcher en eksisterende konto."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:84
msgid "Automatically generate a username and password."
msgstr "Generer automatisk et brugernavn og en adgangskode."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:85
msgid "A password field is provided for the customer."
msgstr "Et adgangskodefelt er tilgængeligt for kunden."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:96
msgid "Automatically matches guest orders to user accounts."
msgstr "Matcher automatisk gæsteordrer med brugerkonti."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:119
msgid "Enable or disable WooCommerce Order Notes field."
msgstr "Aktivér eller deaktiver WooCommerce-feltet for ordre noter."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:135
msgid "Recommended to increase conversions."
msgstr "Anbefales for at øge konverteringer."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:148
msgid "Values are combined into a single address_1 field based on country."
msgstr "Værdier kombineres til et enkelt address_1-felt baseret på land."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:156
msgid "Choose how to display separate address 1 fields."
msgstr "Vælg hvordan separate address 1-felter vises."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:166
msgid "Separate Address Fields is incompatible with Google Address Autocomplete."
msgstr "Separate adressefelter er inkompatible med Google Address Autocomplete."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:171
msgid "Replace first and last name fields with a single full name field."
msgstr "Erstat felterne for fornavn og efternavn med et enkelt felt for fuldt navn."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:178
msgid "Promote selected countries to the top of the countries list."
msgstr "Fremhæv valgte lande øverst på landelisten."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:196
msgid "Validate phone number entry based on selected country."
msgstr "Valider telefonnummerindtastning baseret på valgt land."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:235
msgid "Choose which billing address fields are visible."
msgstr "Vælg hvilke faktureringsadressefelter der er synlige."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:257
msgid "Enable or disable Google Address Autocomplete feature."
msgstr "Aktivér eller deaktiver Google Address Autocomplete-funktionen."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:264
msgid "Enable or disable Fetchify address autocomplete feature."
msgstr "Aktivér eller deaktiver Fetchify adresse-autocomplete-funktionen."

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:280
